Journal of Nonparametric Statistics, (2), 307-331.
X
[2] Koenker, R.W. and d'Orey (1994).  "Remark on Alg. AS 229: Computing Dual
Regression Quantiles and Regression Rank Scores", Applied Statistics, 43, 410-414.
X
X.SA
rq, ranks
